{"tid":678100,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急] 玻利維亞簽證一問","createTime":"2018-05-25T18:59:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T04:47:49.000Z","uid":10766,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"9b4345d6e49f50074d88811f270c83dbdd24c2da","tid":678100,"uid":10766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T18:59:26.000Z","msg":"是咁的 現在係智利聖地牙哥搞去玻利維亞簽證<br />\n12:30pm係領事館交完文件 12:50pm去銀行入埋手續費<br />\n銀行對面有間donut店 忍唔住買咗一個食<br />\n一咬落去 非常軟熟 朱古力味道甜度適中 10分滿分我會俾8分<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/26/025749_4c9e9a9706a53acad99d1e82b90773f0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F26%2F025749_4c9e9a9706a53acad99d1e82b90773f0.jpg&h=1592da1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n食完要去領事館交返張收據<br />\n點知已經關咗門 現在企咗係到應該點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\npassport仲要俾佢收埋"},{"pid":"37a8e04ad523e6ca12c1a472542828d3ed2bb2c7","tid":678100,"uid":2718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T19:19:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幫推"},{"pid":"b067f29b266adb50457c35df289bf3fcd1f1d306","tid":678100,"uid":46225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T19:20:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"761a44207bcdd768324d9f86efe7481a6ddeb2d4","tid":678100,"uid":23037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T19:22:12.000Z","msg":"係咪放飯啊"},{"pid":"f34ff49a592772cc709897e36f2d5639d1ee5739","tid":678100,"uid":33703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T19:37:00.000Z",